mark_rowname <- function(DEGs){
  rownames(DEGs) <- DEGs$gene
  return(DEGs)
}

DEGs.BM <- mark_rowname(read.table("../tissues_DEGs/edgeR_DEGs.tissues_a1_BM_vs_nonBM.csv",
